tags.script: a general extension that adds functionality
tags.localization: a localization extension that translates web ui into another language
tags.dropdown: adds a dropdown in the ui
tags.installed: an extension that is already installed
tags.training: new type of training / assists with training.
tags.UI related: enhances the display or user interface experience.
tags.prompting: assists with writing words, for prompts.
tags.editing: an extension that changes images, not using stable diffusion.
tags.manipulations: an extension that changes images with stable diffusion.
tags.online: an extension which requires wifi to use, often API related.
tags.animation: an extension related to creating videos with stable diffusion.
tags.extras: adds new functionality to the extras tab.
